&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Who we are looking for&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are an experienced backend developer with hard-earned production skills.&lt;/li&gt;
